  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study was to assess whether the behavior, anxiety, and pain of pediatric
      patients during dental treatment improves when a cartoon film is viewed or a videogame is
      played as methods of distraction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
